{"tid":1448852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:15.000Z","uid":262317,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09d0c965ef86c2bd3d309e5e3417fe0e2d83248f","tid":1448852,"uid":262317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=04562779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n<br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=df6dca34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"c38c2b3e5855fe96ba554ea7b18044104d284cd2","tid":1448852,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85a03577890766b42baab94ac0ce1dbc27e4675c","tid":1448852,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00e858a0e9017e5e867455acd9d93ee0dc471a5c","tid":1448852,"uid":128930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cba954d7a374ab1a2c0d202ea35f03478fa72d2d","tid":1448852,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"721,811"},{"pid":"4074e99bce1af6a4de67399471432a4cf950c3a6","tid":1448852,"uid":84614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s